President Muhammadu Buhari attended the Democracy Day celebrations at the Eagle Square in Abuja on Monday. Ahmad Lawan, senate president; Femi Gbajabiamila, speaker house representatives; Ibrahim Tanko Muhammad, chief justice of the federation; former President Goodluck Jonathan, and Bola Tinubu, APC presidential candidate, attended the event. See pictures below. <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-711488" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220613_134541.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="1000" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-711489" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220613_134543.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="1000" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-711490" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220613_134548.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="1000" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-711491" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220613_134712.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="1000" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-711492" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220613_134744.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="1000" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-711500" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220613_135936.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="700" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-711502" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220613_135930.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="1192" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-711504" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220613_135927.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="782" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-711505" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220613_135922.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="988" />